flowRoot.flowPara: To create the background image (Inkscape instructions in brackets):
• Select the item with ID 'bgbox' (Edit → Find, set ID = 'bgbox', tick 'include locked')
• Ensure that the Export Area is 'selection'
• Convert the saved PNG to BMP in Gimp or similar.
To create the title image, follow the instructions above, except select the item with ID 'titlebox' and ensure the export size is 493x58.
